{"tid":546434,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"到底講嘢有懶音仲算唔算係香港人？","createTime":"2018-01-31T13:52:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T14:56:23.000Z","uid":92255,"like":31,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"01c0c90dd087918fd446aba2b0c692e1dc3b4f0a","tid":546434,"uid":92255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T13:52:09.000Z","msg":"話說今日食飯，聽到隔離枱嗰兩條契弟係咁用廣東話講港式粗口，討論j過幾多條女。<br />\n<br />\n本來都冇乜嘢，但係佢哋兩個講嘢都好多懶音/鄉音。<br />\n<br />\n諗諗下又覺得好矛盾，懶音都算係香港獨有，但係講嘢有懶音同5P仔女有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到底講嘢有懶音先係正宗香港人定係講正音先係正宗香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 講正音先係正宗香港人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 講嘢有懶音先係正宗香港人"},{"pid":"ec06ccaf039b429033ced473ebfc442b68d7290e","tid":546434,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T13:54:48.000Z","msg":"...."},{"pid":"33e8767d51db10b70be4680ec56beef826a7e114","tid":546434,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T13:55:40.000Z","msg":"...."},{"pid":"257ec94231b376f75ec69394c35dbbb12c80efd5","tid":546434,"uid":138658,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T13:57:37.000Z","msg":"岩牙"},{"pid":"09d215259f5846e657bacf57121dd468d2686a4b","tid":546434,"uid":50328,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T13:59:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43274acc962be844d1b71822efd14f8e71d6bae2","tid":546434,"uid":92255,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"09d215259f5846e657bacf57121dd468d2686a4b","tid":546434,"uid":50328,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T13:59:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T14:02:15.000Z","msg":"why not both<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢哋嘅對話你聽到會覺得好&quot;銀&quot;耳"},{"pid